==制作==
===开发===
1993年6月，[[哥伦比亚影业|哥伦比亚影业]]一举击败众多电影公司，夺下凯森回忆录的电影版权<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/1993/film/news/wick-col-nab-rights-to-girl-bio-108233/|title=Wick, Col nab rights to 'Girl' bio|last=Frook|first=John Evan|publisher=Variety|date=1993-06-28|accessdate=2020-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200514173858/https://variety.com/1993/film/news/wick-col-nab-rights-to-girl-bio-108233/|archive-date=2020-05-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同样打算买版权的莱德最终与制片人{{tsl|en|Douglas Wick|道格拉斯·威克}}合作，将项目打造成{{le|明星助推器|Star vehicle}}。然而，影片随后落入长达5年的[[制作困境|制作困境]]，当时已经写好的三个剧本都无法让莱德和威克满意，两人的理由是凯森的书很难翻译成电影。莱德看过曼高德的处女作《[[爱你的心|爱你的心]]》，希望找他导演<ref>{{cite web|url=https://archive.nytimes.com/www.nytimes.com/library/film/111499girl-film.html|title=Winona Ryder: Mining Her Memories to Play a Troubled Soul|last=Conant|first=Jennet|publisher=The New York Times|date=1999-11-14|accessdate=2020-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200326152247/https://archive.nytimes.com/www.nytimes.com/library/film/111499girl-film.html|archive-date=2020-03-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1998年中旬，莱德、威克和曼高德定下最终的开拍剧本，哥伦比亚为了让莱德完成恐怖片《{{le|驱魔人 (2000年电影)|Lost Souls (2000 film)|驱魔人}}》，将制作时间推迟到1999年初<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/1998/film/news/ryder-toplines-souls-for-ryan-s-prufrock-1117478338/|title=Ryder toplines ‘Souls’ for Ryan’s Prufrock|last=Petrikin|first=Chris|publisher= Variety |date=1998-07-10|accessdate=2020-07-14}}</ref>。

===选角===
由于电影界不缺乏女演员，许多年轻演员都决定参加电影。[[麗絲·韋花絲潘|麗絲·韋花絲潘]]、[[姬絲汀娜·莉芝|姬絲汀娜·莉芝]]、[[姬蒂·荷姆絲|姬蒂·荷姆絲]]、[[葛雷琴·莫爾|葛雷琴·莫爾]]、[[姬·韓遜|姬·韓遜]]、{{le|艾丽西亚·维特|Alicia Witt}}、[[莎拉·波莉|莎拉·波莉]]和[[罗丝·麦高恩|罗丝·麦高恩]]均参与未具名角色的试镜。曼高德曾在采访中直言“这可是唯一一部不需要脱衣服的体面作品”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://ew.com/article/1998/10/23/behind-scenes-girl-interrupted/|title=Behind the scenes of 'Girl, Interrupted'|last=Laine|first=Tricia|publisher=Entertainment Weekly|date=1998-10-23|accessdate=2020-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200531163122/https://ew.com/article/1998/10/23/behind-scenes-girl-interrupted/|archive-date=2020-05-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

曼高德也联络[[寇特妮·洛芙|寇特妮·洛芙]]出演丽莎一角，联络[[艾拉妮絲·莫莉塞特|艾拉妮絲·莫莉塞特]]出演另一个角色<ref>{{cite web|url=https://theface.com/culture/oral-history-of-girl-interrupted-james-mangold|title=An oral history of Girl, Interrupted|last=Taylor|first=Trey|publisher=The Face |date=2019-12-24|accessdate=2020-07-14}}</ref>。[[帕克·波西|帕克·波西]]放弃了角色<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2018/jul/31/parker-posey-interview-arthouse-hollywood-comic-memoir-ageist-sexist-industry|title=Parker Posey: ‘I didn’t think I would work again – so I wrote a book’|last=Lee|first=Benjamin|publisher=The Guardian|date=2018-07-31|accessdate=2020-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191009153221/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2018/jul/31/parker-posey-interview-arthouse-hollywood-comic-memoir-ageist-sexist-industry|archive-date=2019-10-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[莉莉·索碧斯基|莉莉·索碧斯基]]签约黛西一角，但在开拍前几个礼拜因收到《{{le|圣女贞德 (迷你剧)|Joan of Arc (miniseries)|圣女贞德}}》迷你剧的邀约而推掉角色<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/1998/voices/columns/cbs-skeds-arc-friends-in-salary-huddles-1117488310/|title=CBS skeds ‘Arc’; ‘Friends’ in salary huddles|publisher=Variety |date=1998-11-09|accessdate=2020-07-14}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/1998/film/news/players-59-1117488582/|title=Players|publisher=Variety|date=1998-11-16|accessdate=2020-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714052733/https://variety.com/1998/film/news/players-59-1117488582/|archive-date=2020-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===摄制===
[[File:Beechmont_Harrisburg_PA_Hospital.JPG|thumb]]
影片主要于1999年初在[[宾夕法尼亚州|宾夕法尼亚州]]{{le|梅卡尼克斯堡 (宾夕法尼亚州)|Mechanicsburg, Pennsylvania|梅卡尼克斯堡}}及[[哈里斯堡|哈里斯堡]]的{{tsl|en|Harrisburg State Hospital|哈里斯堡州立医院}}取景<ref name=filming>{{cite web|work=PennLive|title=The filming of 'Girl, Interrupted' in central Pa. in 1999|url=https://www.pennlive.com/galleries/BKHTSBSSQFB7BONRHOUKXJFAU4/|last=Kiner|first=Deb|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200530194849/https://www.pennlive.com/galleries/BKHTSBSSQFB7BONRHOUKXJFAU4/|archive-date=2020-05-30}}</ref>。梅卡尼克斯堡因市貌古旧，老药店直接叫“Drugs”，给能电影带来时代感而被选中。其中一则预告片中火车沿着{{tsl|en|State Street Bridge (Harrisburg, Pennsylvania)|州街大桥}}驶向哈里斯堡，[[賓夕法尼亞州議會大廈|賓夕法尼亞州議會大廈]]清晰可见<ref>{{cite web |title=Information on the filming of Girl, Interrupted at Harrisburg State Hospital |url=http://www.rootsweb.com/~asylums/harrisburg_pa/index.html |website=Rootsweb |accessdate=2020-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080905022519/http://www.rootsweb.com/~asylums/harrisburg_pa/index.html |archive-date=2008-09-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。影片还在[[雷丁_(宾夕法尼亚州)|雷丁]]的{{le|雷丁公共博物馆|Reading Public Museum|公共博物馆}}取景。

==评价==
===专业评价===
[[File:Angelina_Jolie.jpg|thumb]]凭借影片夺得[[奥斯卡最佳女配角奖|奥斯卡最佳女配角奖]]。]]
《移魂女郎》获得影评人褒贬不一的评价，而朱莉的表现受到好评<ref name=rotten/>。[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]给予114条评论打出54%的新鲜度，网站共识指出：“安吉丽娜·朱莉表现出色，但《移魂女郎》总体上被薄弱、可以猜测的情节拖累了，没能抓住原著的力量”<ref name=rotten>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/girl_interrupted |title=Girl, Interrupted Movie Reviews, Pictures |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2020-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190515160802/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/girl_interrupted/ |archive-date=2019-05-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]评论32条，得分51/100，表示“褒贬不一或口碑平平”<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/video/titles/girlinterrupted?q=girl |title=Girl, Interrupted |website=Metacritic |accessdate=2020-05-30}}</ref>。

《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》的斯蒂芬·霍尔顿（{{lang|en|Stephen Holden}}）认为：“《移魂女郎》是一部小而精的时代剧，对与精神病调情的懒惰、放纵女生持固执、艰难地爱的态度：你可以把自己变疯狂，或者克服它。你自己选择<ref>{{cite news |url=https://archive.nytimes.com/www.nytimes.com/library/film/122199girl-film-review.html |title= `Girl, Interrupted': Stop Your Whining, Little Girl |newspaper=The New York Times |date=1999-12-21|last=Holden|first=Stephen|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200328213129/https://archive.nytimes.com/www.nytimes.com/library/film/122199girl-film-review.html|archive-date=2020-03-20}}</ref>。”[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]的汤姆·科茨（{{lang|en|Tom Coates}}）写道：“《移魂女郎》是对凯森回忆录的体面改编，经过抛光打磨，好让观众更加适应光泽，而不是粗粝<ref>{{cite web|last=Coates|first=Tom |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/films/2001/06/28/girl_interrupted_1999_review.shtml |title=Girl, Interrupted |publisher=BBC |date=2001-06-28|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190717120742/http://www.bbc.co.uk/films/2001/06/28/girl_interrupted_1999_review.shtml|archive-date=2019-07-17}}</ref>。”《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》的肯尼斯·杜兰（{{lang|en|Kenneth Turan}}）批评原著小说的改编剧本，认为它“艰难地应付对《[[飛越瘋人院|飛越瘋人院]]》显而易见的标准剧情的仿造”，但也承认莱德和朱莉的表演对电影有帮助，“一直很有诚意，有时会故意这样做......两位女演员有强烈的连结，确保角色真实，即便她们参与的剧情片并非总是达到这个标准<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1999-dec-21-ca-45952-story.html|work=Los Angeles Times|date=1999-12-21|title=Following 'Cuckoo's' Flight Path|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200530202639/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1999-dec-21-ca-45952-story.html|archive-date=2020-05-30|last=Turan|first=Kenneth|access-date=2020-07-24}}</ref>。”

[[有线电视新闻网|有线电视新闻网]]的保罗·塔塔拉（{{lang|en|Paul Tatara}}）批评电影的剧本几乎没有在对白中体现自我反思：“每个女孩都有明显的怪癖，像个练球一样拖拉。”他总结：“不过还好编剧兼导演詹姆斯·曼高德的《移魂女郎》是年度最佳电影，但坏消息是如果要这么认为，你必须是一位高度敏感的17岁女孩”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnn.com/1999/SHOWBIZ/Movies/12/28/review.girlinterrupted/index.html|publisher=CNN|last=Tatara|first=Paul|title=Review: 'Girl, Interrupted' -- Committed drama|date=1999-12-28|dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20031219232658/https://www.cnn.com/1999/SHOWBIZ/Movies/12/28/review.girlinterrupted/index.html|archive-date=2003-12-19}}</ref>。[[罗杰·伊伯特|罗杰·伊伯特]]批评影片没有聚焦所呈现的主题：“影片基本上聚焦于角色和行为，尽管有些戏份的表演很出色，但似乎没有达到目的。这就是为什么结局这么让人不满意的原因：剧情没有体现影片本来可以解决的角色冲突，反倒变成情景剧了<ref>{{cite web|work=Chicago Sun-Times|last=Ebert|first=Roger|title=Girl, Interrupted movie review|date=2000-01-14|dead-url=no|url=https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/girl-interrupted-2000|archive-url=https://archive.today/20150118225119/http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/girl-interrupted-2000|archive-date=2015-01-18|access-date=2020-07-24}}</ref>。”

《[[Time_Out|Time Out电影指南]]》夏洛特·奥苏利文（{{lang|en|Charlotte O'Sullivan}}）称赞朱莉表现之余，不忘批评莱德：“每次朱莉没出镜时，影片会有点萎缩，但这真的没关系吗？莱德本该是完美的亮点，她的台词像匕首一样尖锐。然而，这就是我们所闻与所见的鸿沟所在。莱德的眼睛太宽，太妩媚，我们看他和护士瓦莱丽同框时，就知道两人开始拥抱不过是时间问题”<ref>{{Cite web|last=O'Sullivan|first=Charlotte|work=Time Out|title=Girl, Interrupted|url=https://www.timeout.com/film/reviews/70221/girl_interrupted.html|dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121105050933/http://www.timeout.com/film/reviews/70221/girl_interrupted.html|archive-date=2012-11-05}}</ref>。《[[旧金山纪事报|旧金山纪事报]]》的彼得·斯塔克（{{lang|en|Peter Stack}}）没有对影片留下印象，认为这部“糊涂的作品漏掉了苏珊娜·凯森自传中最刺耳的基调。影片很娱乐，但不算很有力量<ref>{{cite web|last=Stack|first=Peter|url=https://www.sfgate.com/movies/article/Sappy-Girl-Lacks-Character-Development-2784067.php|title=Sappy `Girl' Lacks Character Development|date=2000-01-14|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200131202429/https://www.sfgate.com/movies/article/Sappy-Girl-Lacks-Character-Development-2784067.php|archive-date=2020-01-31|work=San Francisco Chronicle}}</ref>。”《[[纽约每日新闻|纽约每日新闻]]》的杰米·伯纳德（{{lang|en|Jami Bernard}}）的褒贬不一，给予2/4星评价，认为“莱德经常是躺在床上的皱巴巴、无精打采的人物，尽管这很符合抑郁症的本质，但就电影层面而言并不是最吸引人的印象”，就跟[[乌比·戈德堡|乌比·戈德堡]]和[[凡妮莎·蕾格烈芙|凡妮莎·蕾格烈芙]]的表演一样，都快变成[[友情客串|友情客串]]了<ref>{{Cite news|work=New York Daily News|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/52466940/daily-news/|title='Girl'–it's one long interruption|last=Bernard|first=Jami|date=1999-12-21|p=52|via=Newspapers.com}}</ref>。”

===作者观点===
作者苏珊娜·凯森也批评影片，指责曼高德给剧情发明了一些书上没有的剧情点（例如丽莎和苏珊娜一起私奔），简直是“情景剧式的胡言乱语”<ref>{{cite web|author=Danker, Jared|url=https://www.thejustice.org/article/2003/02/susanna-kaysen-without-interruptions|title=Susanna Kaysen, without interruptions|work=The Justice|dead-url=no|date=2003-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200530200751/https://www.thejustice.org/article/2003/02/susanna-kaysen-without-interruptions|archive-date=2020-05-30}}</ref>。

